    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夕方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That Evening",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（まいったな……）\n（まさか瑠依達があんなことを言い出すなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is difficult…）\n（I never thought Rui group would say something like that…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ちょっといいですか？\nさっき見てもらった振り付けなんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ can I ask you something?\nAbout the choreography we showed you earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7679827055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今のトリエルはBIG4に次ぐ人気アイドルだ）\n（突然活動休止なんてしたら大騒ぎになるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Right now‚ TRINITYAiLE is the most popular idol after BIG4）\n（If they suddenly announce a stop to activities‚ it would be a big issue）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2707258781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すぅーっ……\n{user}さーーーーーん！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Glanceー…\n{user}-sanーーーーー!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.969705097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ！！　びっくりした……\n急に大声を上げてどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! I'm so surprised…\nWhat's wrong with you suddenly yelling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7707262596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "「どうしたんだ」じゃありません。さっきから\n話し掛けてるのに、ずっと上の空じゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not 'What's wrong'. I've been\ntalking to you all this time‚ aren't you thinking about something else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6621951882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "多忙で気もそぞろになるのは分かりますが\n今は目の前の私達に集中して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you're probably busy and out of your mind\nbut right now‚ please focus on what's right in front of you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3376893283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、私達からお願いして練習を見に来てもらった\n訳だし、そんなにキツく言わなくてもいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ we asked him to come and watch our practice‚\nso you don't need to be so harsh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.104059593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、沙季の言う通りだ。見に来ておきながら\n他のことに気を取られていた俺が悪い。すまなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ Saki is right. It's my fault I came to see you‚\nbut I distracted by something else. I'm sorry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？\nひょっとして、何か悩みがあるんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…?\nIs there something bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6284496547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 72.4333337148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら私に相談なさい\nお姉さんの私が華麗に悩みを解決して差し上げますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If so‚ please talk to me\nAs your one-san‚ I'll solve your problems elegantly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.504059593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんって……\nすずちゃんは私達の中で一番年下ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One-san…\nSuzu-chan‚ you're the youngest of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1400929054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういう気構えで話を聞くということですわ！\nほら、さっさと悩みを告白なさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I mean‚ I'm going to listen to the story with that kind of feeling!\nCome on‚ tell me your troubles!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8707262596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えっとねー、今日のおやつのドーナツは\nもちもちとサクサクのどっちにしようか迷ってるんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey heyー‚ for today's donut snack‚\nI'm wondering whether to get a chewy or a crispy one~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9089365562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "両方食べればいいでしょう！\n誰も芽衣の悩みなんて聞いていませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can eat both!\nNo one asked about Mei's troubles!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1707262596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど！\nさすがすずにゃん、両方食べることにするよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see!\nAs expected Suzu-nyan‚ I'll have both!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.936578234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "話が脱線してるわよ\n{user}さんが困ってるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're getting off topic\n{user}-san is in trouble",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ははっ……いや、おかげで肩の力が抜けたよ\nすず、心配してくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… No‚ I feel a little better now\nSuzu‚ thanks for worrying about me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9749663592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。みんなにも無関係な話じゃないし\n知っておいた方がいいかもしれないな。実は今朝――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. It's not unrelated to everyone\nI thought it might be good for you to know. Actually‚ this morning――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5416330259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few hours ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0050338665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2385928391
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 143.3219261724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします！\nトリエルの芸能活動を休止させて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please!\nPlease suspend TRINITYAiLE's entertainment activities!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8416330259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことだ？\nまさかアイドルを辞めるつもりなのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's going on?\nAre you really planning on quitting being an idol!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4749663592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "辞める訳ないやん。休止期間中に一から鍛え直して\n一回り成長して戻ってくるつもりなんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. We're planning on training from beginning during our break\nand coming back a whole new level of growth",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1082996925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストは厳しい環境に身を置くことで\n大きく成長しました。私達もそれにならいたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest grew a lot by putting themselves\nin a tough environment. We want to follow that too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私達がサニピを超えるには、月ストと同じ……\nいえ、それ以上に自らを追い込む必要があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we're to go beyond Sunny Peace‚ like the Moon Tempest…\nNo‚ we need to push ourselves more than that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.8082996925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "意気込みは分かった\nだが、活動休止はさすがにやり過ぎじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your decision\nBut‚ isn't stopping activities too much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.1082996925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、芸能活動を止めてメディアの露出がなくなれば\n人気は下降するやろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Certainly‚ once stop entertainment activities and lose media exposure‚\nour popularity will decline",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.1749683937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
