      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。月ストも同じような経験をしたから\n応援してあげたくなるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Moon Tempest has had a similar experience‚\nso it makes me want to support them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 416.1000125886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "もしもの時は私達もトリエルの力になりますから\n彼女達の覚悟を尊重してもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything were to happen‚ we'd be there to support TRINITYAiLE\nSo could you please respect their resolve?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 422.8666792553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "俺も瑠依達の意思は尊重したいが……トリエルの\nスケジュールはかなり先まで埋まっているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd also like to respect Rui group's wishes… but TRINITYAiLE's schedule is\nbooked up far into the future",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 430.3666792553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事に穴を空けると各所に迷惑が掛かるので\nそう簡単に許可出来ないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If somethings goes wrong at work‚ it'll cause trouble everywhere‚\nso I can't allow it that easily",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 437.5072871436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "だったら月ストがトリエルの代役をやろうよ\n休止したトリエルの穴を芽衣達が埋めるの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ Moon Tempest should stand in for TRINITYAiLE\nWe're going to completely fill the gap left by TRINITYAiLE's break!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 444.5072871436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "代役かあ……それなら星見プロのみんなにも\n事情を話して、協力してもらったらどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A stand-in… In that case‚ why don't we explain the situation\nto everyone at Hoshimi Prods. and ask for their cooperation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 452.6000125886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "いいのか？　月ストもただでさえ忙しいのに\nこの上トリエルの仕事まで引き受けるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that okay? Moon Tempest is already busy enough‚\nand now you're taking on TRINITYAiLE's work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 460.4333459219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 463.2814019114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私達もアイドルとして鍛えられましたから\nこれくらいで潰れるほどヤワじゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been trained as idols‚\nwe're not weak enough to be crushed by something like this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 466.6962972991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "なんなら代役の私が大人気になって、トリエルの\nファンとお仕事を根こそぎ奪って差し上げますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll take this chance to become really popular\nand root out TRINITYAiLE's fans and works",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 474.4000125886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルは同じ星見プロの仲間だもんね\n友達が困ってたら助け合うのは当たり前だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is a colleague of Hoshimi Prods.\nIt's only natural to help my colleagues when they're having a trouble",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 483.0584889002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_04-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "仲間で友達か……。分かった。所属アイドルの\nために頭を下げるのもマネージャーの務めだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Friends and colleagues…. Okay. It's also a manager's duty\nto bow his head for his idols",
